name: Change the game
description:
The first collector of this NFT will receive this original painting.
1st collector, please DM me via Twitter @Maks_Denysenko & I'll send it to you!

Change the game
It is difficult to imagine how different paint cores will work together. Acrylic, nitro, water based spray paints one wrong move and it`s all dust or looks too dirty. But in one very best combination it`s abstract magic.

Artwork created by Maksym Denysenko in 2018, 90x90cm Spray paint on canvas 2676x2696 pix.
